Responsibilites:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Manual transaction review</li>
<li>
Investigation of accounts, users and payments</li>
<li>
Assist in building and tweaking automated fraud engine rules</li>
<li>
Work with fraud victims to recover funds and provide information and support</li>
<li>
Work with departments to determine if potential customers comply with the WePay Terms of Service</li>
<li>
Handle chargeback recovery and reporting</li>
<li>
Interact with users whose payments require further information or investigation</li>
