As Senior Sales Engineer / Developer Evangelist you will be helping to bring more customers to the WePay API platform. You will guide our customers through complex technical, regulatory and financial issues to help them integrate with our API. Your daily job will include various activities: architecting payments solutions for our clients; participating in internal product discussions; answering technical questions about our API; attending conferences, hackathons and meetups; building prototype integrations; writing technical marketing materials; and doing many other interesting things. As with anyone else at WePay, you will wear many hats.</p>
