<strong>Ideal candidate:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Experience working with online payments.</li>
<li>
Experience working with developers and/or developing on open APIs.</li>
<li>
Prior startup experience.</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>About WePay:</strong></p>
<p>
WePay is the surprisingly simple way to accept payments online. Our product allows anyone &ndash; merchant, organization, or individual &ndash; to start collecting money faster than any other competitor. WePay has raised $20 million in financing and is backed by August Capital, Highland Capital Partners, Max Levchin (founder of PayPal), Y Combinator and SVAngel. The company is headquartered in Palo Alto, CA and has been featured in The New York Times, The Wall Street Journal, CNN, Fox, and Forbes.</p>
